    <item>
      <title>查尔斯国王诊断癌症后出席复活节仪式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/king-charles-will-attend-easter-service-providing-a-glimpse-of-the-monarch-after-cancer-diagnosis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦（美联社）——周日，国王查理三世在温莎城堡参加复活节仪式后与旁观者握手并聊天，这是他自上个月被诊断患有癌症以来最重要的公开活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/king-charles-will-attend-easter-service-providing-a-glimpse-of-the-monarch-after-cancer-diagnosis</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 09:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯向乌克兰能源设施发射新的无人机攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/war-in-ukraine-odesa-left-in-the-dark-after-latest-russian-airstrikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[地方当局表示，俄罗斯周日袭击了乌克兰南部和远西部的能源设施，几乎每天都进行无人机和导弹袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/war-in-ukraine-odesa-left-in-the-dark-after-latest-russian-airstrikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 09:10:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对党领袖被捕后，数千人在德里举行集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/thousands-attend-a-rally-in-india-s-capital-to-challenge-prime-minister-modi-ahead-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新德里（美联社）——印度反对党联盟周日举行大规模集会，发起竞选活动，批评总理纳伦德拉·莫迪政府在下个月的全国大选前压制对手并破坏民主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/thousands-attend-a-rally-in-india-s-capital-to-challenge-prime-minister-modi-ahead-of-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 09:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教宗在圣彼得广场主持复活节周日弥撒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/pope-overcomes-health-concerns-presides-over-blustery-easter-sunday-mass-in-st-peter-s-square</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马（美联社）——周日，教皇方济各在经历了长达冬季的呼吸道疾病困扰后重整旗鼓，带领约 6 万人参加复活节庆祝活动，强烈呼吁加沙停火以及俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的囚犯交换。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/pope-overcomes-health-concerns-presides-over-blustery-easter-sunday-mass-in-st-peter-s-square</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 08:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马萨诸塞州前美国议员威廉·德拉亨特去世，享年 82 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/former-us-rep-william-delahunt-of-massachusetts-has-died-at-age-82</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马萨诸塞州长期担任美国众议员的威廉·D·德拉亨特 (William D. Delahunt) 是民主党的坚定支持者，他推迟了自己从华盛顿退休的时间，以帮助通过前总统巴拉克·奥巴马 (Barack Obama) 的立法议程，他的家人宣布，他因长期患病去世。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/former-us-rep-william-delahunt-of-massachusetts-has-died-at-age-82</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 08:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安在土耳其城市的地方民意调查中面临激烈的竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/erdogan-faces-tight-race-in-turkish-cities-in-local-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安及其执政党在周日的全国地方选举中陷入了激烈的角逐，这是在赢得新任期 10 个月后对领导人权力的一次关键考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/erdogan-faces-tight-race-in-turkish-cities-in-local-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
